{"id":40189,"date":"2024-02-18T10:25:00","date_gmt":"2022-12-18T04:55:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=40189"},"modified":"2023-01-03T14:01:31","modified_gmt":"2023-01-03T08:31:31","slug":"mid-century-modern-sofa-design","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/mid-century-modern-sofa-design\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Iconic Mid-Century Modern Sofa Designs For The Living Room And Beyond"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Bring home the sleek looks and clean lines of a mid-century modern sofa. Check out these designs and ideas for inspiration.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mid-century modern design is all about reinventing. Its essence lies in reimagining how your furniture can support your frame and rediscovering the new ways it can transform your space. It is especially true for mid-century modern sofa designs. Known for their rectangular, clean shapes and subtle curves, the simplistic sofas from this era create a perfect focal point for your living room and can easily pair with other interior design styles and aesthetics.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hence, when you are designing or renovating your living room, you must start with the pi\u00e8ce de r\u00e9sistance: the sofa. Here are some of our designer-approved mid-century modern style sofas for you to get started.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Minimalist Mid-Century Modern Wood Frame Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for something unique in your sofa selection, this is it. This wooden frame sofa is so minimalist that it seems like it is made of only cloud-soft cushions. It perfectly blends with the designs of the side table and coffee table and compliments the wooden accent of the wall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202102\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Mid-century modern wood frame sofa which is extremely minimalistic\" class=\"wp-image-40193\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202102\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202102\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202102\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202102\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Minimalist wooden-frame sofa for a clean look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mid-Century Modern Leather Sofa Is A Bachelor Pad Staple<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A stylish bachelor pad is incomplete without a leather sofa. This tan-coloured mid-century modern sectional sofa flawlessly complements the exposed brick wall and the grey accent wall, bringing the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/industrial-style-interior-design-ideas-for-your-home\/\">industrial-style interiors<\/a> alive. The geometric patterned colourful area rug adds much-needed vibrancy to the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202133\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Leather-Sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A mid-century modern sofa made of leather which is a bachelor pad staple\" class=\"wp-image-40198\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202133\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Leather-Sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202133\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Leather-Sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202133\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Leather-Sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202133\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Leather-Sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Mid-century modern sofa in industrial-style interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Enhance your living room's interior design with our solutions!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20124603\/enhance-your-living-rooms-interior-design-with-our-solutions.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Grey Contemporary Mid-Century Modern Sofa For A Multicoloured Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colour blocking the walls is in trend these days. Gone are those single-coloured boring walls. People are now fearless about painting their homes in multiple bold colours. So, to balance the vibrancy, you need solid colour furniture. This grey mid-century modern style sofa does the job very well and it\u2019s perfect for small spaces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202127\/A-mid-century-modern-sofa-in-grey-.jpg\" alt=\"A mid-century modern sofa in grey for a multicolored living room\" class=\"wp-image-40197\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202127\/A-mid-century-modern-sofa-in-grey-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202127\/A-mid-century-modern-sofa-in-grey--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202127\/A-mid-century-modern-sofa-in-grey--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202127\/A-mid-century-modern-sofa-in-grey--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Solid colour contemporary mid-century modern sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mid-Century Modern Sofa Set For Chic Living Room Interiors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Its uncluttered, sleek look makes the mid-century modern sofa a cult favourite. This sofa set with a dark green three-seater couch and two tan accent chairs is the epitome of sophistication. If you are in the market for a mid-century modern sofa set that is guaranteed to become a conversational centrepiece, look no further than this set.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202109\/Mid-century-modern-sofa-set-for-chic-living-room-interior.jpg\" alt=\"A Mid-Century Modern Sofa Set with a dark green three-seater couch\" class=\"wp-image-40194\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202109\/Mid-century-modern-sofa-set-for-chic-living-room-interior.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202109\/Mid-century-modern-sofa-set-for-chic-living-room-interior-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202109\/Mid-century-modern-sofa-set-for-chic-living-room-interior-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202109\/Mid-century-modern-sofa-set-for-chic-living-room-interior-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A conversation starter mid-century modern sofa set<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Outdoor Mid-Century Modern Sectional Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you entertain guests often, you deserve a spot that can become the party central of your home. Hence, this rooftop portico does a fantastic job. This long, built-in mid-century modern style L-shaped sectional sofa is perfect for seating more than 5-7 people. Since it is a permanent fixture, the sofa is made of water-resistant material. It\u2019s a perfect setting for a Sunday brunch or a late-night get-together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202055\/mid-century-modern-sectional-sofa-for-outdoor.jpg\" alt=\"A Mid-Century Modern Sectional Sofa for outdoor\" class=\"wp-image-40192\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202055\/mid-century-modern-sectional-sofa-for-outdoor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202055\/mid-century-modern-sectional-sofa-for-outdoor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202055\/mid-century-modern-sectional-sofa-for-outdoor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202055\/mid-century-modern-sectional-sofa-for-outdoor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An outdoor mid-century modern sectional sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End to end home interiors solutions for stress free living\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/07152137\/end-to-end-home-interiors-solutions-for-stress-free-living.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mid-Century Modern Wood Frame Sofa For Balcony Lounge<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sip your tea or coffee in this balcony lounge in the morning or unwind at the end of the day with a glass of wine and your latest read. This sleek mid-century modern teak sofa is your perfect companion. Get inspired by this Mediterranean-style <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/balcony-design\/\">balcony design <\/a>to give yours a makeover.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202048\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-for-balcony-lounge.jpg\" alt=\"A Mid-Century Modern Wood Frame Sofa For Balcony Lounge\" class=\"wp-image-40191\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202048\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-for-balcony-lounge.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202048\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-for-balcony-lounge-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202048\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-for-balcony-lounge-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202048\/Mid-century-modern-wood-frame-sofa-for-balcony-lounge-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Lightweight mid-century modern wood frame sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mid-Century Modern Sleeper Sofa For The Poolside Patio<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Lounge, relax, and unwind after taking a dip in the pool in these boho-style mid-century modern sleeper sofas. These weather-proof and lightweight sofas are also great for entertaining guests during a poolside party.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202115\/Mid-century-modern-sleeper-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A mid-century modern sleeper Sofa for the poolside patio\" class=\"wp-image-40195\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202115\/Mid-century-modern-sleeper-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202115\/Mid-century-modern-sleeper-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202115\/Mid-century-modern-sleeper-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202115\/Mid-century-modern-sleeper-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Boho-style mid-century modern sleeper sofas<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mid-Century Modern Curved Sofa Is Boldness Personified<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for ways to experiment with your sofa design and make a statement, this type of mid-century modern curved sofa could be your perfect choice. The bold combination of blue and pink magically uplifts the white living room vibe. And completing the look is the metal, marble-top coffee table that takes the space to a whole new dimension.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202139\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Curved-Sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A Mid-Century Modern Curved Sofa to make a statement\" class=\"wp-image-40199\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202139\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Curved-Sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202139\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Curved-Sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202139\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Curved-Sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/13202139\/A-Mid-Century-Modern-Curved-Sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Be bold with a blue mid-century modern sofa\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope these mid-century modern sofa designs have given you ample ideas for the perfect piece for your home. Explore more of our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/\">living room interior design ideas<\/a>. But if you are unsure or want a customised design, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">get in touch with our expert interior 